				</div>
					</div>
		<ul class="relatedStories--list" data-total="3">
			<li class="relatedStories--item" data-number="1" data-progressive="true" data-component="photo"><div class="card" data-number="1"><a class="hdn-analytics" href="https://projects.sfchronicle.com/2020/coronavirus-map/" data-hdn-analytics="related_stories|link-92130|article-15193899|1"><div class="card--image"><img data-src='https://s.hdnux.com/photos/01/10/70/24/19105062/20/gallery_medium.jpg'></div><div class="card--headline"><h4 class="card--headline-title">Coronavirus Map: Tracking COVID-19 cases across California</h4></div></a></div></li><li class="relatedStories--item" data-number="2" data-progressive="true" data-component="photo"><div class="card" data-number="2"><a class="hdn-analytics" href="https://www.sfchronicle.com/bayarea/article/Coronavirus-live-updates-news-bay-area-15192855.php" data-hdn-analytics="related_stories|article-15192855|article-15193899|2"><div class="card--image"><img data-src='https://s.hdnux.com/photos/01/11/37/35/19265395/7/gallery_medium.jpg'></div><div class="card--headline"><h6 class="card--retSection">Local</h6><h6 class="card--headline-byline">By Lauren Hernandez, Rachel Swan, Jill Tucker, Rita Beamish, Kate Galbraith and Ron Kroichick</h6><h4 class="card--headline-title">Coronavirus live updates: UCSF health workers headed to New...</h4></div></a></div></li><li class="relatedStories--item" data-number="3" data-progressive="true" data-component="photo"><div class="card" data-number="3"><a class="hdn-analytics" href="https://www.sfchronicle.com/bayarea/article/coronavirus-bayarea-what-you-need-know-15000563.php" data-hdn-analytics="related_stories|article-15000563|article-15193899|3"><div class="card--image"><img data-src='https://s.hdnux.com/photos/01/10/64/36/19089317/9/gallery_medium.jpg'></div><div class="card--headline"><h6 class="card--retSection">Local</h6><h6 class="card--headline-byline">Chronicle Staff Report</h6><h4 class="card--headline-title">Coronavirus hits Bay Area: What residents need to know</h4></div></a></div><